comments: Amazing professor! One of the best at GCC. He made the subject very interesting and very knowledge when you ask questions.

I took Soc. Sc. 132 during summer semester with prof Nguyen. I ought to admit that he is a great professor. All the material he lectured and talked about, I found very interesting and unique. Being so young, he has lots of knowledge and definitely knows the subject. He friendly answers all the questions. I highly recommend to take his class...

Professor Nguyen was very knowledgeable. He would answer any questions that you have, and very reasonable with his approach to teaching. If you go to class, print out the lecture notes, then you will do well. Thanks, Prof. Nguyen for all of the food you bought for us the last day of class! That was very generous of you :)
Love this guy! He\'s really the best prof in GCC.. Super nice and helpful... really cool teacher! 2 thumbs up... Sooo glad i got into his class. =)

coolest teacher ive ever had. the book is optional. he posts the notes online. he takes attendace only 8 times. his lectures with power point, very easy to follow and his test are open note and you can take the test online. no comprehensive final just regular chapter test. best teacher by far. highly recommended
Cool instructor, used a lot of what he lectured on the test. Easy class as long as you pay attention and do some reading.
